<h2>Bus travel advice </h2>
<ul>
    <li>You can use bus routes 15, 42, 78, 100 and RV1 to reach the Tower of London.  These routes stop within 5 to 10 minutes' walking distance of the Tower of London.</li>
    <li>Bus routes to and from the Tower of London may be busier than usual</li>
    <li>To plan ahead on the day <a href="/plan-a-journey/index">visit Journey Planner</a> </li>
    <li>For the latest information on bus services <a href="https://twitter.com/TfLBusAlerts">follow &#64;TfLBusAlerts on Twitter</a></li>
</ul>
<h2>River travel advice</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Tower Millennium Pier is likely to be busier than usual. Allow extra time for journeys or take alternative routes if possible</li>
    <li>For the latest information on TfL's river services <a href="https://twitter.com/TfLriver">follow &#64;TfLRiver on Twitter</a></li>
</ul>
<h2>Road travel advice - drivers</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Please avoid driving to the area if possible. If driving is your only option, be aware that there is no parking at the Tower of London and roads will be busy</li>
    <li>Road closures and diversions will be in place due to the Lord Mayor's Show and Remembrance Day events especially around City of London and Westminster</li>
    <li><a href="/roads/status/?disruptionIds=TIMS-65264">View current disruptions</a>. For the latest information on how London roads are operating, check before you travel and <a href="https://twitter.com/TfLtrafficnews">follow &#64;TfLTrafficNews on Twitter</a></li>
</ul>
<h2>Road travel advice - cyclists</h2>
<ul>
    <li>
    You can travel to Tower Hill by bike - Cycle Superhighway 3 will remain open throughout</li>
    <li>If you plan on taking your bike on public transport, remember that restrictions apply including on train operating companies outside London. Read <a href="/modes/cycling/cycling-in-london/bikes-on-public-transport">our guidance regarding bikes on public transport</a> or your train operating company's website  </li>
    <li>For Santandar Cycle Hire docking station availability use our <a href="/modes/cycling/santander-cycles/find-a-docking-station">live docking station map</a></li>
    <li><a href="http://www.twitter.com/SantanderCycles">Follow &#64;SantanderCycles on Twitter</a> for the latest updates</li>
</ul>
</div>
 
      
        
          
